## if step (6) is missing

間

        MAGNITUDE 0.8
        CERTAINTY 0.9

        we build it

        Lemma quotient_pi1_of_simply_connected:
          X simply connected
          G acts freely, properly discontinuously
          → π₁(X/G) ≅ G

        Proof sketch:
          universal cover of X/G is X
          deck transformations of universal cover = π₁
          deck transformations = G (by construction)
          
        this is ~50 lines in Lean
        not ~200 for path lifting
        
        the winding number EMERGES from this
        we don't construct it
        
        ◊

